data.title: Rich-mom politics, social scheming and a delicious murder mystery collide with a bang in @kieranscottauthor's REGRETS ONLY, a fast-paced,...
data.meta_description: 170 likes, 3 comments - kristinharmel on January 9, 2023: "Rich-mom politics, social scheming and a delicious murder mystery collide with a bang in @kieranscottauthor's REGRETS ONLY, a fast-paced, juicy read full of flirtation, danger, and lies. Out this week, it's a perfect dose of twisty, decadent fun. Also new this week, @natashalesterauthor's THE THREE LIVES OF ALIX ST. PIERRE is the story of an orphan turned WWII spy turned fashion icon in Paris. Says Kate Quinn, "The Three Lives of Alix St. Pierre braids espionage, fashion, and a broken-but-unbowed heroine together into one fascinating tale."".
